    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** ** Precomposition with an essentially surjective functor is faithful *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Section faithfull_precomposition_essential_surjective.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n  (** Quoting the HoTT Book:\n\n  Lemma. If [A], [B], [C] are precategories and [H : A \u2192 B] is an\n  essentially surjective functor, then [(\u2013 \u2218 H) : (B \u2192 C) \u2192 (A \u2192 C)]\n  is faithful. *)\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Context `{fs : Funext}.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Variables A B C : PreCategory.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Variable H : Functor A B.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Context `{H_is_essentially_surjective : IsEssentiallySurjective A B H}.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Lemma isfaithful_precomposition_essentially_surjective_helper\n        (F G : Functor B C)\n        (T U : NaturalTransformation F G)\n        (a : A) (b : B)\n        (f : H a <~=~> b)\n        (H' : T oR H = U oR H)\n  : T b = U b.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": [
        {
          "_type": "goal",
          "name": null,
          "conclusion": "T b = U b",
          "hypotheses": [
            {
              "_type": "hypothesis",
              "names": [
                "fs"
              ],
              "body": null,
              "type": "Funext"
            },
            {
